description:
With the yes man skill, Alexa will provide positive comments to your questions. When in doubt, ask yea man! Give it a shot! 

Just say, "Alexa, ask yea man (any yes or no question here)
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Yea Man if I should do this.
name: Yea Man
shortDescription: Everyone needs a yea man in their life. Just ask yea man any questions and it will give you a answer.
